        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>The summer is finally here, in the northern hemisphere at least. I'm going to take advantage of the quieter period to try something a little bit different with <em>OM&amp;HB</em> between now and September. Rather than always writing long pieces, and then sending them as newsletters, I'm going to get back into the old fashioned blog groove of writing shorter links posts to interesting news, and then summarise those posts in weekly newsletters to you.</p><p>After all, nobody wants to find a whole pile of unread emails building up in their inbox after a break, do they?</p><p>I'll reassess at the end of August (or sooner if my open rate plummetsâ€¦), but do let me know if this revised approach works for you.</p>"
